### Summary

Add a styled Agenda section to `DetailPanel.tsx` that renders for `event` and `meeting` Things, sourcing items from `thing.data.agenda_items` (the existing flexible JSON field — no backend migration needed). The section uses `w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary` bullet dots per the design file and is placed above Notes.

